# Weather Dashboard

A Weather Dashboard application built using JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and Chart.js to visualize weather data with dynamic and animated charts. The dashboard displays temperature trends over a period, provides current weather information, and supports Celsius and Fahrenheit unit conversions. It also provides chatbot to ask weather and nonweather related queries.

## Features

- Dynamic line chart to display temperature trends using Chart.js
- Delay animation effect on vertical bar chart and doughnut chart for engaging visual representation
- Drop animation effect on line chart for engaging visual representation
- Responsive and mobile-friendly design
- Option to toggle between Celsius and Fahrenheit temperature units
- Fetches real-time weather data from a weather API

## Technologies Used

- **HTML5 , CSS3 , JavaScript (ES6+) , Chart.js , Weather API , Gemini API**

## Instructions to Run
- Just run index.html file
